Question: One image shows a gauzy white canopy that drapes the front half of a bed from a cone shape suspended from the ceiling.

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show a gauzy white canopy?')

ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the canopy suspended from the ceiling in a cone shape?')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER5}')

FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
```
